{"tid":479453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"總自殺率降　青少年自殺率增　男青少年自殺率增55%　超越總平均","createTime":"2017-11-25T06:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T23:55:30.000Z","uid":47714,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b69f4427dd9d0885eb31cadd22ebdd35cc4e9485","tid":479453,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T06:42:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1284284-20160909.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1284284-20160909.htm&d=N8XfqDuzeZiIqZa3Yt1piywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=78d2b39f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1284284-20160909.htm&h=4cf61f9d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1284284-20160909.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港大學香港賽馬會防止自殺研究中心估測，2015年香港每10萬人有12.6人死於自殺，自2003年以來，自殺率持續超過10年呈下降趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n但中心公布最新自殺數據顯示，在2015年每10萬名15至24歲青少年就有8.5人死於自殺，較2014年的6.2人高，當中男性青少年自殺率升幅比較明顯，由2014年的8.3人上升至2015年的12.9人。<br />\n<br />\n中心研究發現，自殺學生大多與親友欠缺良性溝通，多宗個案都曾在遺書中表示，自己長期受自殺意念困擾，但不敢告訴他人。"},{"pid":"5ca42d096ef8829a99fcf2b2005d52550bfb1d7e","tid":479453,"uid":121213,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T06:49:38.000Z","msg":"係香港做男人真係好撚辛苦<br />\n讀完書出黎做野得個一萬幾人工  返6日仲要晚晚日開ot  想溝條女都難<br />\n溝d港女 佢地仲要求你有車有樓<br />\n唔撚講咩d衣食住行<br />\nd親戚 朋友  家人 都比壓力你  拎你同人比較<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nthis is 香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408163b3f26e87bd530c003e2eb1b02cbc5fcd2c","tid":479453,"uid":34103,"like":5,"dislike":34,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T07:03:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba9cdc7008a37a5273c74b46dda01fb1b202a8fa","tid":479453,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T07:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是但啦<br />\n700萬人，多佢一個唔多，小佢一個唔小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母,你唔